52:06.804 --> 52:09.053
but the truth is,

52:09.053 --> 52:10.970
I don't.

52:12.387 --> 52:14.929
I am damn good at my job,

52:14.929 --> 52:18.303
but I want to work
for someone I believe in.

52:18.303 --> 52:21.178
